<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 14:07:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特拉维夫大使馆为被杀的哈马斯领导人哈尼亚降半旗致哀，以色列召见土耳其特使</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/israel-summons-turkish-envoy-after-tel-aviv-embassy-lowers-flag-for-slain-hamas-leader/00000191-133c-d5cd-abfd-b73e00f00000</link><description>以色列内政部长还宣布，他打算吊销耶路撒冷阿克萨清真寺一名在布道中哀悼哈尼亚的传教士的居留许可；土耳其总统埃尔多安宣布周五为哈尼亚全国哀悼日</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 13:56:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/israel-summons-turkish-envoy-after-tel-aviv-embassy-lowers-flag-for-slain-hamas-leader/00000191-133c-d5cd-abfd-b73e00f00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方在参加抗议活动三周后在家中逮捕了反政府活动人士</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-arrest-anti-govt-activist-at-home-three-weeks-after-protest/00000191-11f6-d015-adf7-f9fe0ca10000</link><description>这位 64 岁的活动人士上个月在他帮助组织的一次反政府抗议活动中首次被捕，本周又在他的家中被捕。 “警察进了我家？为什么？如果他们打电话来，我就会亲自到达车站，”他说</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 12:23:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-arrest-anti-govt-activist-at-home-three-weeks-after-protest/00000191-11f6-d015-adf7-f9fe0ca10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列司法部长：许多以色列人现在明白司法改革的必要性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-justice-minister-many-israelis-now-understand-the-need-for-judicial-overhaul/00000191-129c-dbcf-afb9-57fdc82c0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡政府试图削弱法院的策划者之一、司法部长亚里夫·莱文在右翼会议上表示，“现在是所有 64 个联盟成员充分致力于此的时候了”</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 11:16:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-justice-minister-many-israelis-now-understand-the-need-for-judicial-overhaul/00000191-129c-dbcf-afb9-57fdc82c0000</guid></item><item><title>自 1992 年以来，以色列体育取得了长足的进步，Inbar Lanir 就是证明</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/london-2012/olympics-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-sports-have-come-a-long-way-since-1992-and-inbar-lanir-is-proof/00000191-1239-d015-adf7-fa3f93a30000</link><description>自雅埃尔·阿拉德 32 年前获得银牌以来，以色列已获得 13 枚奥运会奖牌。女子奥林匹克运动和以色列女运动员的地位一直处于这一进步的最前沿</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 10:18:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/london-2012/olympics-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-sports-have-come-a-long-way-since-1992-and-inbar-lanir-is-proof/00000191-1239-d015-adf7-fa3f93a30000</guid></item><item><title>两名半岛电视台记者在以色列对加沙的袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/.premium/two-al-jazeera-journalists-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-gaza/00000191-122a-d015-adf7-fa3ea7000000</link><description>半岛电视台阿拉伯语记者伊斯梅尔·古尔（Ismail Al-Ghoul）和他的同事摄影师拉米·阿尔里菲（Rami Al-Rifi）周三在哈马斯政治领袖伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚（Ismail Haniyeh）在加沙的家附近的沙蒂难民营进行报道后被杀，哈马斯政治领袖伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚（Ismail Haniyeh）当天早上在德黑兰被杀。据半岛电视台报道，他们的汽车成为以色列国防军的目标</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 09:15:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/.premium/two-al-jazeera-journalists-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-gaza/00000191-122a-d015-adf7-fa3ea7000000</guid></item><item><title>我如何发现自己陷入了定居者大屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-i-found-myself-inside-a-settler-pogrom/00000191-0eb0-dba6-a59d-0efb03b80000</link><description>在参与寻找一名在约旦河西岸失踪的以色列青少年的过程中，我亲身体验了无处可去的血腥现实</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 03:23:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/how-i-found-myself-inside-a-settler-pogrom/00000191-0eb0-dba6-a59d-0efb03b80000</guid></item><item><title>哈尼亚遇刺事件明确表明：以色列人质问题并非内塔尼亚胡议程的重中之重</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/.premium/haniyehs-assassination-made-it-clear-israeli-hostages-are-not-top-of-netanyahus-agenda/00000191-0f51-dba6-a59d-0f5b3e970000</link><description>尽管存在升级的危险，哈马斯政治局局长被杀还是提高了以色列总理的地位。他可以用它来罢免国防部长加兰特，后者支持一项包括开火的协议</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 03:00:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/.premium/haniyehs-assassination-made-it-clear-israeli-hostages-are-not-top-of-netanyahus-agenda/00000191-0f51-dba6-a59d-0f5b3e970000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡遇刺庆祝活动结束后，以色列将不得不为此买单</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-will-have-to-pick-up-the-tab-after-netanyahus-assassination-celebrations/00000191-0f50-dba6-a59d-0f5ba6ff0000</link><description>哈马斯和真主党高级官员被杀的第二天，地区战争的可能性变得更大，人质交易面临受挫的危险——至少目前是这样。 ■ 内塔尼亚胡将如何对待公众给予他的赞誉？ ■ 将军们现在是民主的守门人</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 03:00:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-will-have-to-pick-up-the-tab-after-netanyahus-assassination-celebrations/00000191-0f50-dba6-a59d-0f5ba6ff0000</guid></item><item><title>报告：真主党将设备转移到贝鲁特；以色列部长获得卫星电话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article-live/biden-netanyahu-discuss-new-u-s-military-deployments-to-support-israel/00000191-10e4-dc1a-a1b7-19fcd0a00000</link><description>拜登：哈尼亚被杀无助于实现停火 ■ CNN：美国官员表示，伊朗可能利用代理人攻击美军，以回应哈尼亚被刺杀事件 ■ 白宫表示，拜登和内塔尼亚胡讨论了美国支持以色列的军事部署 ■ 真主党领袖纳斯鲁拉警告要对以色列最近的暗杀行动进行报复：“你不知道你已经跨越了红线”</description><pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 02:42:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-02/ty-article-live/biden-netanyahu-discuss-new-u-s-military-deployments-to-support-israel/00000191-10e4-dc1a-a1b7-19fcd0a00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队指挥官允许定居者对希伯伦族长墓进行翻修，并向上级隐瞒</title>