-communitys-name/00000191-0e29-d4cf-afb5-4efd817b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 18:38:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/an-israeli-war-of-vengeance-in-lebanon-not-in-the-druze-communitys-name/00000191-0e29-d4cf-afb5-4efd817b0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔·巴齐莱 (Netta Barzilai) 演唱《Fuego》：理论上，以色列欧洲歌唱大赛冠军的首张专辑非常棒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-08-01/ty-article-review/.premium/netta-singing-fuego-israeli-eurovision-winners-debut-album-is-superb-in-theory/00000191-08e8-dc54-a7dd-ffeab09b0000</link><description>在她的第一张完整专辑中，也是她的母语希伯来语的第一张专辑中，这位“玩具”热门制作人试图摆脱定义她职业生涯的激烈竞争</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 18:33:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-08-01/ty-article-review/.premium/netta-singing-fuego-israeli-eurovision-winners-debut-album-is-superb-in-theory/00000191-08e8-dc54-a7dd-ffeab09b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列新闻频道所有者的家遭到燃烧弹袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/home-of-israeli-news-channels-owner-attacked-with-molotov-cocktail/00000191-0dad-dba6-a59d-0fefa8260000</link><description>拥有 Channel 12 的公司 Keshet 表示，对 David Wertheim 家的袭击是右翼针对媒体、特别是该频道长期煽动的结果。</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 18:21:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/home-of-israeli-news-channels-owner-attacked-with-molotov-cocktail/00000191-0dad-dba6-a59d-0fefa8260000</guid></item><item><title>以色列因担心英特尔将宣布裁员而做好准备</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-braces-amid-fears-that-intel-will-announce-job-cuts/00000191-0d77-dbed-a5f9-dff7ed920000</link><description>随着这家美国芯片巨头建造更多工厂，它必须在其他地方削减开支。以色列人还将寻找英特尔是否真的停止在以色列建设新工厂的线索</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 18:19:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-braces-amid-fears-that-intel-will-announce-job-cuts/00000191-0d77-dbed-a5f9-dff7ed920000</guid></item><item><title>以色列研究表明智能手表可以警告您患有新冠病毒或即将发生偏头痛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-study-shows-smartwatches-can-warn-you-have-covid-or-a-migraine-is-about-to-happen/00000191-0e9d-d4cf-afb5-4edd06130000</link><description>特殊的传感器使特拉维夫大学的科学家能够在患者出现症状之前识别出新冠病毒、流感和链球菌性咽喉炎的迹象。下一个目标：偏头痛和高血糖</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 18:17:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-study-shows-smartwatches-can-warn-you-have-covid-or-a-migraine-is-about-to-happen/00000191-0e9d-d4cf-afb5-4edd06130000</guid></item><item><title>如果以色列能杀死伊朗的哈尼亚，肯定能把115人从加沙带回国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-01/ty-article/.highlight/if-israel-can-kill-haniyeh-in-iran-it-can-surely-bring-115-people-back-home-from-gaza/00000191-0eea-dc54-a7dd-ffeaf9260000</link><description>已经300天了，我不知道那些关键人物，那些谈论彻底胜利的人，是否已经哭了。我不确定他们是否意识到每个人质的名字都蕴含着灵魂</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 18:11:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-01/ty-article/.highlight/if-israel-can-kill-haniyeh-in-iran-it-can-surely-bring-115-people-back-home-from-gaza/00000191-0eea-dc54-a7dd-ffeaf9260000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 300 天：以色列呼吁公民在国外谨慎行事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-300-israel-calls-on-citizens-to-exercise-caution-abroad/00000191-0ed4-d782-af93-1fdc9f490001</link><description>总理内塔尼亚胡表示，以色列已做好应对任何情况的准备，并将与美国总统拜登进行对话 ■ 西方外交官警告称，贝鲁特和德黑兰发生暗杀事件后，战争风险有所增加 ■ 真主党领袖纳斯鲁拉：“我们在所有领域都进入了一个新阶段” ■ 以色列证实，哈马斯军事首领穆罕默德·德伊夫 (Mohammed Deif) 在 7 月以色列国防军对汗尤尼斯 (Khan Yunis) 的袭击中丧生 ■ 以下是战争 300 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 16:51:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-300-israel-calls-on-citizens-to-exercise-caution-abroad/00000191-0ed4-d782-af93-1fdc9f490001</guid></item><item><title>《纽约时报》报道称，哈马斯领导人哈尼亚被德黑兰宾馆安置的炸弹炸死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/hamas-leader-haniyeh-killed-by-bomb-planted-in-tehran-guesthouse-nyt-report-says/00000191-0e65-d782-af93-1ffd4fcc0000</link><description>该报告与早前关于这位政治领袖在一次有针对性的空袭中丧生的猜测相矛盾。伊朗官员称这次暗杀是伊朗情报和安全方面的灾难性失败，也是革命卫队的重大尴尬</description><pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 15:54:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-01/ty-article/.premium/hamas-leader-haniyeh-killed-by-bomb-planted-in-tehran-guesthouse-nyt-report-says/00000191-0e65-d782-af93-1ffd4fcc0000</guid></item></channel></rss>